Description
-=-=-=-=-=-=

Microsoft Office 2007 Blue Edition is a version of Microsoft Office you may not have heard of. That is because of one of two reasons.
Reason 1: Blue Edition is only available to Microsoft Technicians
Reason 2: Blue Edition is a version of Microsoft Office 2007 Enterprise that has had the activation removed.

Installation Details
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

To install Office, go into 'Office 2007 Enterprise Blue Edition' folder and run setup.exe
To install Microsoft Works to Word Converter, go into 'Microsoft Works to Word Converter' folder and run Works632_en-US.msi
To install Microsoft Office Compatibility Pack for Word, Excel and PowerPoint File Formats, go into 'Microsoft Office Compatibility Pack for Word, Excel and PowerPoint File Formats' folder and run FileFormatConverters.exe
